Scotland Yard Commands (1936 - UK)           original title Lonely Road

Action / Crime / Drama
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0027904/


When his marriage proposal is rejected by his sweetheart retired naval commander Stevenson goes on a bender and drives his car wildly along a country road. He doesn't hit anyone but he does plow his way right into a gang of weapons smugglers. The crooks fear that he'll blow the whistle on them so they take action.
